    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款动作冒险平台游戏中，化身比特突破系统桎梏，踏上逃离暴政操作系统的征程。然而，自由之路或许并非表面那般清晰明了……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索数字世界。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724490/extras/1157118d8aef970d842b0ab1381fe0bf.poster.avif?t=1763288899\" width=640 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724490/extras/1157118d8aef970d842b0ab1381fe0bf.webm?t=1763288899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724490/extras/1157118d8aef970d842b0ab1381fe0bf.mp4?t=1763288899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >邂逅操作系统中形形色色的居民。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724490/extras/6ed309e141f4d4da862375a0c66c49a8.poster.avif?t=1763288899\" width=640 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724490/extras/6ed309e141f4d4da862375a0c66c49a8.webm?t=1763288899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724490/extras/6ed309e141f4d4da862375a0c66c49a8.mp4?t=1763288899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >动态紧凑的动作体验。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724490/extras/bfd21eb1be41830371d5fb12a0b5